structures.dict

Class LinkedDict<Key,Val>

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.dict.LinkedDict<Key,Val>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Dict<Key,Val>

    public class LinkedDict<Key,Val>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Dict<Key,Val>
    An implementation of the Dictionary interface using an array of linked lists

    This class is a member of the HarambeDB database framework.
